Package co.edu.escuelaing.arep.networking.httpserver

Class MimeType

java.lang.Object
co.edu.escuelaing.arep.networking.httpserver.MimeType
public class MimeType
extends java.lang.Object
Map file extensions to MIME types. Based on the Apache mime.types file. http://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/

    • registerMimeType

      public static void registerMimeType​(java.lang.String ext, java.lang.String mimeType)
      Registers MIME type for provided extension. Existing extension type will be overriden.
      Parameters:
      ext - - Extension of MimeType file
      mimeType - - Type of content

    • getMimeType

      public static java.lang.String getMimeType​(java.lang.String ext)
      Returns the corresponding MIME type to the given extension. If no MIME type was found it returns 'application/octet-stream' type.
      Parameters:
      ext - - Extension of MimeType file
      Returns:
      the MimeType content

    • getExt

      public static java.lang.String getExt​(java.lang.String mimeType)
      Simply returns Ext or null if no Mimetype is found.
      Parameters:
      mimeType - - Type of content
      Returns:
      The extension of the mimeType

    • lookupMimeType

      public static java.lang.String lookupMimeType​(java.lang.String ext)
      Simply returns MIME type or null if no type is found.
      Parameters:
      ext - - Extension of MimeType file
      Returns:
      the MimeType content
